videos.description: Stone Smartt keeps it on the option and runs in a 10-yard touchdown to increase Old Dominion's lead on Virginia.

videos.description: Stone Smartt hits a wide-open Matt Geiger, who breaks a couple of tackles for a 47-yard Old Dominion touchdown.
